snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Minamata Scene Chat: More of Our Reaction and Analysis
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp / Minamata / Controversy / Amber Heard / 

We continue our chat about Minamata and continue our analysis of a scene that we're showing you. As you know, there has been controversy over this film as the director claims MGM has suppressed it in the US due to the Johnny Depp controversy regarding Amber Heard. 

Part 1 where we show the full scene and discuss: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sCDPSrxYnRs 

Part 2 where we continue our discussion: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vVu5ChtFEWE 

Subscribe to me channel for Part 4 and more Depp & celeb videos.
